Class HighScoreEntry

java.lang.Object
com.comp2042.game.stats.HighScoreEntry
public final class HighScoreEntry extends Object
Immutable value object describing a single leaderboard row (score, mode, clear time, timestamp).

Instances are normally created by HighScoreService when a game completes but the class also exposes recreate(int, String, long, long) for reconstructing entries from disk.
